# LUNARIS Asset License

Everything in this `assets/` directory (art, audio, music, fonts created for
the project) is licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International license (CC BY-SA 4.0), unless a
file or subdirectory contains its own LICENSE/README stating otherwise.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode

Attribution: "LUNARIS contributors" with a link to the project repository.

Why assets are licensed separately from code (which is MIT — see /LICENSE):
this is the OpenTTD / 0 A.D. code/asset split. It keeps the engine maximally
reusable while ensuring the project's creative identity stays share-alike.
Third-party assets may only be added if their license is CC BY-SA-compatible
and is recorded in an adjacent ATTRIBUTION file.
